article_text:
March 14, 2016 10:00 PM

If you're a fan of Amy Schumer-- you have the chance to see her perform live in Rochester this spring.

The comedian/ actress is touring and is making a stop at Blue Cross Arena on Friday, May 6. Tickets will go on sale on Friday starting at 10 a.m.
